But the law will not allow it, Pompey;
nor it
shall not be allowed in Vienna.

div2.stage:
Enter, on one side, DUKE disguised as before;

on the other, ELBOW, and Officers

with POMPEY.

sp.p:
Indeed, it does stink in some sort,
sir;
but yet, sir, I would prove--

Good my lord, be good to me;

your honour 
is accounted a merciful man;

good my lord.

You rogue, I have been drinking all
night;
I am not fitted for't.

My lord, here comes the rascal I
spoke of;
here with the provost.
